3243  MVMapView.prototype.getThemeIndex = function(themeBasedFOI)
3244  {
3245    for (var i = 0; i < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; i++)
3246    {
3247      if (MVUtil.strTrim(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.name) == MVUtil.strTrim(themeBasedFOI.name))
3248      {
3249        return i+1;
3250      }
3251    }
3252    MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.getThemeIndex", "MAPVIEWER-05510", MVUtil.strTrim(themeBasedFOI.name), this.errorHandler);    
3253  }

3255  /**
3256    This method gets the original display order of the theme-based FOI layer. This
3257    can be used to reset themes back to their original display order using setThemeIndex.
3258    
3259    @param {MVThemeBasedFOI}  themeBasedFOI ThemeBasedFOI is an object that defines
3260                  the theme-based FOI layer.
3261    @returns the original theme-based FOI layer index(1-100)
3262    @type int
3263  */
3264  MVMapView.prototype.getOrigThemeIndex = function(themeBasedFOI)
3265  {
3266    for (var i = 0; i < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; i++)
3267    {
3268      if (MVUtil.strTrim(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.name) == MVUtil.strTrim(themeBasedFOI.name))
3269      {
3270        return this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].origIndex;
3271      }
3272    }
3273    MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.getOrigThemeIndex", "MAPVIEWER-05510", MVUtil.strTrim(themeBasedFOI.name), this.errorHandler);    
3274  }

3276  /**
3277    This method sets the display index of the theme-based FOI layer.
3278    @param {MVThemeBasedFOI}  themeBasedFOI an MVThemeBasedFOI object that defines 
3279                     the theme-based FOI layer.
3280    @param {int}     index Display index(1-100)
3281    @returns   None
3282    @type void
3283  */  
3284  MVMapView.prototype.setThemeIndex = function(themeBasedFOI, index)
3285  {
3286    /*if (index > this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length) 
3287      index = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length;*/
3288    if (index > 100) 
3289      index = 100;
3290    if (index < 1)
3291      index = 1;
3292    for (var i = 0; i < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; i++)
3293    {
3294      if (MVUtil.strTrim(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.name) == MVUtil.strTrim(themeBasedFOI.name))
3295      {
3296        //reorder themes
3297        while(i+1 < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length && i+1 < index)
3298        {
3299          var tmp = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i] ;
3300          this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i] = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i+1] ;
3301          this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i+1] = tmp ;
3302          i++;
3303        }
3304        while(i+1 > index)
3305        {
3306          var tmp = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i] ;
3307          this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i] = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i-1] ;
3308          this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i-1] = tmp ;
3309          i--;
3310        }
3311        break ;
3312      }
3313    } 
3314    for (var j = 0; j<this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; j++)
3315    {
3316     this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].div.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130;
3317     if(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].transImageLayer)
3318       this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].transImageLayer.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130 + 1;
3319     if (this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].transImageLayer && this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].FOIType != 1 && 
3320         this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].themebasedfoi.minClickableLevel <= this.zoomLevel)
3321       this.transparentLayer.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130 + 1;
3322     this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].currentIndex = j;
3323    }
3324  }

3330    @returns   None

3384  /**
3385    This method enables event propagation from the info window. When event 
3386    propagation is enabled, events such as mouse clicks and keyboard strokes
3387    are propagated to the rest of the map client instance after they are handled
3388    inside the info window. When event propagation is diabled, events are trapped 
3389    inside the info window and not propapated outside. The latter is usally 
3390    prefered when the info window needs to handle some events that should only 
3391    occur to the map decoration itself. By default, event propagation for info
3392    window is disabled.
3393    @param {boolean}  enabled true (enable event propagation) or false (disable event propagation).
3394    @returns   None
3395    @type void
3396  */
3397  MVMapView.prototype.enableInfoWindowEventPropagation = function(enabled)
3398  {
3399    if(!this.infoLayer)
3400       this.infoLayer = new MVInfoLayerControl(this, "1") ;
3401    this.infoLayer.enableEventPropagation(enabled);
3402  }

3404  /**
3405  @private
3406  */
3407  MVMapView.prototype.refreshThemeBasedFOIs = function(clearFirst)
3408  {
3409    if (this.infoLayer)
3410      this.infoLayer.hideTopNode();
3411    this.do_GetMinMaxLonLat();   
3412    var lc = 0; 
3413    for (lc = 0; lc < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; lc++)
3414    {
3415      var layer = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[lc];   
3416      if (layer.FOIType != 1)
3417      {
3418        layer.clearTransImageLayer() ;
3419      }
3420      var themeBBox = this.getThemeBBoxAndSetThemeWindowSize(layer) ;
3421      var foiData = layer.themebasedfoi.getFOIData();
3422      if (foiData != null)
3423      {
3424        if (!layer.boundingThemeLoaded && 
3425            !layer.themebasedfoi.autoRefreshing && foiData[0].gtype % 10 == 1 &&
3426            layer.themebasedfoi.maxWholeImageLevel < this.zoomLevel)//do not need refresh
3427        {
3428          layer.clearAll();
3429          layer.div.style.display = 'none';
3430          layer.themebasedfoi.minX = layer.minX = themeBBox[0];
3431          layer.themebasedfoi.minY = layer.minY = themeBBox[1];
3432          layer.themebasedfoi.maxX = layer.maxX = themeBBox[2];
3433          layer.themebasedfoi.maxY = layer.maxY = themeBBox[3];
3434          layer.zoomLevel = this.zoomLevel;
3435        
3436          var lleft = Math.ceil((layer.minX - this.mapWindowMinLon)* this.pixPerX);
3437          var ltop = -Math.ceil((layer.maxY - this.mapWindowMaxLat)* this.pixPerY); 
3438          MVUtil.setLeftTop(layer.getContainer(), lleft, ltop);
3439          layer.centerX = this.mapCenterX;
3440          layer.centerY = this.mapCenterY;     
3441          for(var i = 0; i< foiData.length; i++)
3442          {
3443            layer.displayFoi(foiData[i]);
3444          }
3445          layer.makeFOIsVisiable();
3446          layer.boundingThemeLoaded = false;
3447          layer.loading = false ;
3448          continue;
3449       }
3450     }
3451      
3452     layer.refreshFOIs(this,themeBBox[0], themeBBox[1], themeBBox[2], themeBBox[3], clearFirst, false, null, true);
3453    }
3454  }

3456  /**
3457  @private
3458  */
3459  MVMapView.prototype.getMeshCoordsMin4ThemeBasedFOIQuery = function (_lon, _lat)
3460  {
3461    var coords = {"x":0,"y":0};
3462    var mX = Math.floor((_lon - this.msi.getMinX())/this.msi.getTileWidth(this.zoomLevel));
3463    var mY = Math.floor((_lat - this.msi.getMinY())/this.msi.getTileHeight(this.zoomLevel));
3464    coords.x = this.msi.getMinX() + mX * this.msi.getTileWidth(this.zoomLevel);
3465    coords.y = this.msi.getMinY() + mY * this.msi.getTileHeight(this.zoomLevel);
3466    return coords;
3467  }
3468  /**
3469  @private
3470  */
3471  MVMapView.prototype.getMeshCoordsMax4ThemeBasedFOIQuery = function (_lon, _lat)
3472  {
3473    var coords = {"x":0,"y":0};
3474    var mX = Math.floor((_lon - this.msi.getMinX())/this.msi.getTileWidth(this.zoomLevel));
3475    var mY = Math.floor((_lat - this.msi.getMinY())/this.msi.getTileHeight(this.zoomLevel));
3476    coords.x = this.msi.getMinX() + (mX + 1) * this.msi.getTileWidth(this.zoomLevel);
3477    coords.y = this.msi.getMinY() + (mY + 1 ) * this.msi.getTileHeight(this.zoomLevel);
3478    return coords;
3479  }
3480  /**
3481  @private
3482  */
3483  MVMapView.prototype.removeAllThemeBasedFOI = function()
3484  {
3485    if(this.displayed)
3486    {
3487       for (var lc = 0; lc < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; lc++)
3488         this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[lc].setVisible(false,false);
3489       this.refreshThemeBasedFOIs(false);
3490    }
3491        
3492    while (this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length > 0)
3493    {
3494      this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length - 1].destroy();
3495      this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length - 1] = null; 
3496      this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.pop();   
3497    }
3498    while (this.transparentLayer.childNodes.length > 0)
3499    {
3500     this.transparentLayer.removeChild(this.transparentLayer.childNodes[0]);
3501    }
3502  }

3504  /**
3505    This method removes a theme-based FOI layer from the map.
3506    @param {MVThemeBasedFOI} themebasedfoi the MVThemeBasedFOI object that 
3507     specifies the theme-based FOI layer to be removed.
3508    @returns   None
3509    @type void
3510  */
3511  MVMapView.prototype.removeThemeBasedFOI = function(themebasedfoi)
3512  {
3513    if(!themebasedfoi)
3514     return ;
3515    for (var lc = 0; lc < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; lc++)
3516    {
3517      if (themebasedfoi == this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[lc].getThemeBasedFOI())
3518      {
3519        this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[lc].destroy();
3520        this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.splice(lc,1);  
3521        break;
3522      }
3523    }
3524    //remove the transparent layer
3525    for (var a = 0; a < this.transparentLayer.childNodes.length; a++)
3526    {
3527      if (this.transparentLayer.childNodes[a].id == themebasedfoi.name)
3528      {
3529        this.transparentLayer.removeChild(this.transparentLayer.childNodes[a]) ;
3530        a--;
3531      }
3532    }       
3533    for (var j=0; j<this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; j++)
3534    {
3535     this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].div.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130;
3536     if (this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].transImageLayer && this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].FOIType != 1 && 
3537         this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].themebasedfoi.minClickableLevel <= this.zoomLevel)
3538     {
3539       this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].transImageLayer.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130 + 1;
3540       this.transparentLayer.style.zIndex = j*2 + 130 + 1;
3541     }
3542     this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[j].currentIndex = j;
3543    }
3544  }
3545  /**
3546  @private
3547  */
3548  MVMapView.prototype.scrollThemeBasedFOIs = function ()
3549  {
3550    if (this.infoLayer)
3551      this.infoLayer.hideTopNode();
3552    this.do_GetMinMaxLonLat();
3553    var lc = 0;
3554    var infoLayerRefreshed = false;
3555    for (lc = 0; lc < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; lc++)
3556    {
3557      var layer = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[lc];
3558      if (//!layer.isLoading() && 
3559          (
3560          this.mapWindowMinLon < layer.getMinX()||
3561          this.mapWindowMinLat < layer.getMinY()||
3562          this.mapWindowMaxLon > layer.getMaxX()||
3563          this.mapWindowMaxLat > layer.getMaxY()) && layer.themebasedfoi.autoRefreshing)
3564      {
3565        var themeBBox = this.getThemeBBoxAndSetThemeWindowSize(layer) ;
3566        if (layer.FOIType != 1)
3567        {
3568          layer.clearTransImageLayer() ;
3569        }
3570        layer.refreshFOIs(this,themeBBox[0],themeBBox[1],themeBBox[2],themeBBox[3], true, false);
3571      }
3572      else if(layer.boundingThemeLoaded)
3573      {
3574        var themeBBox = this.getThemeBBoxAndSetThemeWindowSize(layer) ;
3575        layer.refreshFOIs(this,themeBBox[0],themeBBox[1],themeBBox[2],themeBBox[3], true, false);
3576        //layer.refreshFOIs(this,0,0,0,0,true, false);
3577      }
3578    }
3579    if (this.mapWindowMinLon < this.indFOIsControl.minX||
3580        this.mapWindowMinLat < this.indFOIsControl.minY||
3581        this.mapWindowMaxLon > this.indFOIsControl.maxX||
3582        this.mapWindowMaxLat > this.indFOIsControl.maxY) 
3583     {
3584 
3585       var xOffset = (this.indFOIsControl.getLayerWidth() - this.getPaneWidth())*0.5/this.pixPerX;
3586       var yOffset = (this.indFOIsControl.getLayerHeight() - this.getPaneHeight())*0.5/this.pixPerY;   
3587       this.indFOIsControl.refreshIndFOIs(this.mapWindowMinLon - xOffset, 
3588                                          this.mapWindowMinLat - yOffset,
3589                                          this.mapWindowMaxLon + xOffset, 
3590                                          this.mapWindowMaxLat + yOffset);    
3591       this.refreshGroupFOIs(false);
3592     }
3593 	else if( this.wraparound ) // the foi generated by the tools need refresh when the user drag more than a quarter of the earth  
3594 	{
3595 	    var xOffset = (this.indFOIsControl.getLayerWidth() - this.getPaneWidth())*0.5/this.pixPerX;
3596 		var totalMoveLeft = xOffset - ( this.mapWindowMinLon - this.indFOIsControl.minX );
3597 		var totalMoveRight = xOffset - (  this.indFOIsControl.maxX - this.mapWindowMaxLon);
3598 		var totalMove = totalMoveLeft>0?totalMoveLeft:totalMoveRight;
3599 		
3600 		var minRefreshDistance = (this.msi.coverMaxX - this.msi.coverMinX) / 4;
3601 		
3602 		if(totalMove > minRefreshDistance)
3603 		{
3604 		   var yOffset = (this.indFOIsControl.getLayerHeight() - this.getPaneHeight())*0.5/this.pixPerY;   
3605 		   this.indFOIsControl.refreshIndFOIs(this.mapWindowMinLon - xOffset, 
3606 											this.mapWindowMinLat - yOffset,
3607 											this.mapWindowMaxLon + xOffset, 
3608 											this.mapWindowMaxLat + yOffset);    
3609 		}			
3610 	}
3611    if (!infoLayerRefreshed)
3612    {
3613      this.infoLayer.refresh(this.mapWindowMinLon, this.mapWindowMinLat, this.mapWindowMaxLon,
3614          this.mapWindowMaxLat, this.getPaneWidth(), this.getPaneHeight());
3615      this.infoLayer2.refresh(this.mapWindowMinLon, this.mapWindowMinLat, this.mapWindowMaxLon,
3616          this.mapWindowMaxLat, this.getPaneWidth(), this.getPaneHeight()) ;
3617      infoLayerRefreshed = true;
3618    }   
3619  }

3629  /** 
3630  This methods sets the default info window style. The info window can be rendered in one 
3631  of the following three styles: InfoWindowStyle1 and InfoWindowStyle2.
3632  The default info window style is InfoWindoStyle1. The info window style can be furthure
3633  customized when InfoWindowStyle1 is chosen. The customization parameters are specified
3634  in the styleParameters object, which might have the following attributes.
3635    <UL>
3636      <LI>hideCloseButton, a boolean that specifies whether to hide the close button.</LI>
3637      <LI>closeButtonImageURL, a string that specifies the URL of the close button image.</LI>
3638      <LI>bodyStyle, a CSS string that sepcifies the info window border width, border color, 
3639          background color and etc. Example: "border:1px;border-color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF".</LI>
3640      <LI>titleBarStyle, a CSS string that specifies the title bar text color, background-color, 
3641          text font, font size, font weight and etc. Example: "color:#ffffff;background-color:#483D8B;font-weight:bold;font-family:Aria;font-size:14".</LI>
3642      <LI>contentStyle, a CSS string that sepcifies the info window content style such as content padding, text font, color and etc. 
3643          background color and etc. Example: "border:1px;border-color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF".</LI>
3644      <LI>coneStyle, a CSS string that specifies the color and opacity of the cone. Example:"background-color:#99CC33;opacity:30".</LI>
3645      <LI>offset, a integer that specifies the pixel offset of the info window relative to the anchor point.</LI>
3646    </UL>
3647   <p>Here is a usage example.</p>
3648   <pre>
3649   var parameters = {hideCloseButton:true,
3650                     closeButtonImageURL:"/mapviewer/fsmc/images/infoicons/close_circle.gif",
3651                     bodyStyle:"border:2px;border-color:#FF0000;background-color:#FFFFFF",
3652                     titleBarStyle:"background-color:#8794A3",
3653                     contentStyle:"padding:10px",
3654                     coneStyle:"background-color:#00CCAA;opacity:30",
3655                     offset:10} ;
3656   mapview.setDefaultInfoWindowStyle("InfoWindowStyle1", parameters);
3657   </pre>
3658  *@param  {String} style the name of the info window style. The possible values are 
3659                    "MVInfoWindowStyle1", "MVInfoWindowStyle2" and "MVInfoWindowStyle3". 
3660  *@param  {Object} styleParameters the object that specifies the custom style parameters.
3661  */
3662  MVMapView.prototype.setDefaultInfoWindowStyle = function(style, styleParameters)
3663  {
3664    MVGlobalVariables.defaultInfoStyle = style ;
3665    if(style=="MVInfoWindowStyle1")
3666      MVInfoWindowStyle1.defaultStyleParameters = styleParameters;
3667  }

3670  /**
3671  *This method displays an information window on the map at a specified location. 
3672  *The content of the information window is defined by an HTML string. The application user can 
3673  *close the information window by clicking the close ("X") button inside the window.
3674  *@param  {MVSdoGeometry} point a point MVSdoGeometry object that specifies the location of
3675  the info window on the map, which is defined in the map coordinate system.
3676  If the width and height are omitted, the info window will automatically sized 
3677  to best fit the content. 
3678  
3679  *@param  {string} htmlString an HTML content string to be displayed inside the information window.
3680  *@param   {int} width  the width of the information window in pixels.
3681  *@param  {int} height  the height of the information window in pixels.
3682  *@param {string} style an optional String parameter that specifies the information window style. 
3683           The possible values are "InfoWindowStyle1" or "InfoWindowStyle2". 
3684           By default, all information windows are displayed using "InfoWindowStyle1".
3685  *@param {string} title an optional String parameter that specifies the info window title string. 
3686  *@param  {Object} styleParameters the object that specifies the custom style parameters,
3687           which are effective only when the info window style is "MVInfoWindowStyle1".
3688  *@returns   None
3689  *@type void
3690  */
3691  MVMapView.prototype.displayInfoWindow = function(point, htmlString, width, height, style, title, styleParameters)
3692  {
3693    if(this.infoWindowTimeout)
3694    {
3695      clearTimeout(this.infoWindowTimeout) ;
3696      this.infoWindowTimeout = null ;
3697    }
3698    var mv = this ;
3699    var callBack = function(newPoint)
3700    {
3701      if(newPoint)
3702        point = newPoint ;
3703      mv.infoLayer.showHtmlWindow(htmlString,  point.sdo_point.x, point.sdo_point.y, width, height,style,title, styleParameters);
3704    }
3705    var showInfoWindow = function()
3706    {
3707     if(mv.displayed && !mv.displayTimer && !mv.zoomToTimer && !mv.m_scroll_id)
3708     {
3709       if (!point.srid)
3710         point.srid = mv.srid ;
3711       if (point.srid && (mv.srid != point.srid))
3712         center = mv.transformGeom(point, mv.srid, null, callBack);
3713       else
3714         callBack() ;
3715     }
3716     else
3717       mv.infoWindowTimeout = setTimeout(showInfoWindow, 200) ;
3718    }
3719    showInfoWindow() ;
3720  }

3754    }

3756    {
3757     if(mv.displayed && !mv.displayTimer && !mv.zoomToTimer && !mv.m_scroll_id)
3758     {
3759       if (!point.srid)
3760         point.srid = mv.srid ;

3766     else
3767       mv.infoWindowTimeout = setTimeout(showInfoWindow, 200) ;

3800  /** 
3801  * This function registers a JavaScript function that converts coordinates specified 
3802  * in a coordinate system to coordinates specified in another coordinate system. 
3803  * The registered coordinate transformation function is called whenever such
3804  * coordinate system transformation is needed. For example, when the application
3805  * invokes MVMapView.transformGeom or the application specifies the map center
3806  * in a coordinate system that is different from the map tile layer coordinate system.
3807  * called 
3808  * 
3809  * @param {Object} transformFunction: the function used to transform the coordinates. This function takes the
3810  * X and Y coordinates as the input parameters and returns an object that specifies the result
3811  * coordinates as attributes x and y.
3812  * @param {int}fromSrid: the Srid of the coordinate system from which the tranformation function transforms
3813  * the coordinates.
3814  * @param {int} toSrid: the Srid of the coordinate system into which the tranformation function transforms 
3815  * the coordinates.
3816  */
3817  MVMapView.prototype.addCSTransformFunction= function(transformFunction, fromSrid, toSrid)
3818  {
3819    MVGlobalVariables.addCSTransFunc(fromSrid, toSrid, transformFunction);
3820  }
3821  
3822  /** 
3823  * This method transforms the input geometry from one coordinate system to another
3824  * coordinate system. When this method is called, the map client sends a request to 
3825  * the map tile server, which invokes Oracle Spatial utilities to perform 
3826  * coordinate system transformation and then returns the result to the client.
3827  
3828    <p>When XMLHTTP/XMLHttpRequest objects are enabled, the request for coordinate 
3829    system transformation is sent in synchronous mode and the application javascript
3830    code following this method call will not be executed until the transformation
3831    result is returned from the server. When XMLHTTP/XMLHttpRequest objects are disabled, 
3832    the request is sent in asynchronous mode without pausing for the server side transformation
3833    result. In this case, all application code that depends on the transformation 
3834    result should be packed into a call back function so that it can be executed only after 
3835    transformation result is returned. When the call back function is invoked after the
3836   result is returned, the transformed geometry is passed into the call back function as the only
3837   parameter.</p></p>
3838    
3839    <p>Please refer to {@link #enableXMLHTTP} for more information.
3840  
3841  *@param  {MVSdoGeometry}geometry  the MVSdoGeometry object to be transformed.
3842  *@param {int} toSrid that specifies the SRID of the destination coordinate system.
3843  *@param  {string}mcsURL an optional parameter that specifies the URL of the map tile 
3844  *         server to be used to perform the coordinate system transformation. 
3845  *         If this parameter is omitted, the map tile server associated 
3846  *         with the first map tile layer is used.
3847   @param {function} callBack the call back function that is execuated after the
3848           coordinate system transformation is finished.
3849   @param {String} dataSource the name of the mapviewer data source inside which the server
3850                   side length calculation is to be performed. If omitted, the data source 
3851                   associated with the first map tile layer added is used.
3852   @returns The resulting MVSdoGeometry object when XMLHTTP/XMLHttpRequest objects 
3853            are enabled. Null when XMLHTTP/XMLHttpRequest objects are disabled.
3854   @type     MVSdoGeometry
3855   @see #enableXMLHTTP
3856  */
3857  MVMapView.prototype.transformGeom = function(geometry, toSrid, mcsURL, callBack, dataSource)
3858  {
3859    if(!geometry.srid)
3860    {
3861      if(!this.srid)
3862      {
3863        MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.transformGeom", "MAPVIEWER-05520", null, this.errorHandler) ;
3864        return ;
3865      }
3866      geometry.srid = this.srid ;
3867    }
3868    if(geometry.srid == toSrid)
3869    {
3870      if(callBack)
3871      {
3872        callBack(geometry) ;
3873        return ;
3874      }
3875      else
3876        return geometry;
3877    }
3878    var clientTrans = MVGlobalVariables.getCSTransFunc(geometry.srid, toSrid) ;
3879    /* do client side transformation for point and simple polygon/polyline only*/
3880    if(clientTrans)
3881    {
3882      var geom = null ;
3883      if(geometry.getGType()==1)
3884      {
3885        var result = clientTrans(geometry.getPointX(), geometry.getPointY(), this.errorHandler) ;
3886        geom = MVSdoGeometry.createPoint(result.x, result.y, toSrid) ;
3887      }
3888      else if((geometry.gtype%10==2||geometry.gtype%10==3) &&
3889              geometry.sdo_elem_info.length==3 && geometry.sdo_elem_info[0]==1 && 
3890              (geometry.sdo_elem_info[1]==2||geometry.sdo_elem_info[1]==1003||geometry.sdo_elem_info[1]==2003) &&
3891              geometry.sdo_elem_info[2]==1)
3892      {
3893        var ordinates = MVMapView.transformOrdinates(clientTrans, geometry.sdo_ordinates, this.errorHandler);
3894        geom = new MVSdoGeometry(geometry.gtype, toSrid, geometry.sdo_elem_info, ordinates);
3895      }
3896      if(geom)
3897      {
3898       if(callBack)
3899       {
3900         callBack(geom) ;
3901         return ;
3902       }
3903       else
3904         return geom;
3905      }
3906    }
3907    if (mcsURL)
3908    {}
3909    else if (this.baseURL)
3910    {
3911      if (MVUtil.strEndWith(this.baseURL, '/'))
3912      {
3913        mcsURL = this.baseURL + 'mcserver'; 
3914      }
3915      else
3916      {
3917        mcsURL = this.baseURL + '/mcserver';
3918      }       
3919    }
3920    else
3921    {
3922      MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.transformGeom", "MAPVIEWER-05504", null, this.errorHandler) ;
3923      return ;
3924    }
3925    var localDomain = (MVUtil.isLocalDomain(mcsURL)) ;
3926    var xmlHttp = localDomain || MVMapView.XMLHTTPEnabled ;
3927    if(!xmlHttp && !callBack)
3928    {
3929      MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.transformGeom", "MAPVIEWER-05521", null, this.errorHandler) ;
3930      return null ;
3931    }
3932    //http://localhost:8888/mapviewer/mcserver?request=cstransform&srcsrid=8307
3933    //&dstsrid=8301&geometry=POINT(-122+38)&datasource=mvdemo
3934    //return {"SDO_GTYPE":1,"SDO_SRID":8301,"SDO_POINT":{"X":116.401160316578,"Y":39.8976406312728}}
3935    var request = null;
3936    var finalresult;
3937    var mgeometry;
3938    var mdatasource;
3939    if(dataSource)
3940     mdatasource = dataSource ;
3941    else
3942     mdatasource = this.defaultDataSource;
3943    mgeometry = MVUtil.strReplaceAll(geometry.toString(), "null", "");
3944    if (geometry.getGType() == 1)
3945    {
3946       mgeometry = MVUtil.strReplaceAll(mgeometry, "SdoPointType", "");
3947    }
3948    else
3949    {
3950      // mgeometry = mgeometry.replaceAll("sdo_elem_info_array","").replaceAll("sdo_ordinate_array","");
3951    }
3952    mgeometry = MVUtil.strReplaceAll(mgeometry, " ", "");
3953    var targetURL = mcsURL ;
3954    var csTransUrl = mcsURL ;
3955    var params = "request=cstransform&dstsrid=" +
3956                 toSrid + "&geometry=" + mgeometry ;
3957    if(mdatasource)
3958      params += "&datasource=" + mdatasource;
3959              
3960    var request = null ;
3961    //add MVUtil.closureWrapper for the function to resolve memory leak
3962    var mv = this ;
3963    var transformed = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this,function()
3964    {
3965     if (request.readyState == 4) 
3966     {
3967       if (request.status == 200) 
3968       {
3969         try
3970         {
3971           var resp = request.responseText ;
3972           eval("var result="+resp);
3973           finalresult = result;
3974           if (result.length == 0)
3975           {
3976             result = null;
3977             return;
3978           } 
3979           var geom = null ;
3980           if (finalresult.SDO_GTYPE == 1)
3981           {
3982           //{"SDO_GTYPE":1,"SDO_SRID":8301,"SDO_POINT":{"X":-121.995862386656,"Y":37.9928186627724}}
3983             geom = MVSdoGeometry.createPoint(finalresult.SDO_POINT.X, finalresult.SDO_POINT.Y, finalresult.SDO_SRID);
3984           }
3985           else
3986           {
3987             //{"SDO_GTYPE":2,"SDO_SRID":8301,"SDO_ELEM_INFO":[1,2,1],
3988             //"SDO_ORDINATES":[-122.495840026876,37.7928326537697,-122.445840561553,37.8428317942925,-122.405844359684,37.8228300198945]}
3989             geom = new MVSdoGeometry(2000 + finalresult.SDO_GTYPE, finalresult.SDO_SRID,finalresult.SDO_ELEM_INFO,finalresult.SDO_ORDINATES, null)
3990           }
3991           result = null;    
3992         }
3993         catch(e)
3994         {
3995           MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.transformGeom", "MAPVIEWER-05523", request.responseText, mv.errorHandler) ;
3996           return ;
3997         }
3998         if(callBack)
3999           callBack(geom) ;
4000         if(xmlHttp)
4001           return geom ;
4002       }
4003     }
4004    });
4005   
4006    try 
4007    {
4008      request = MVUtil.getXMLHttpRequest(xmlHttp);
4009      if(callBack || !xmlHttp)
4010        request.onreadystatechange = transformed ;
4011      request.open("POST", MVUtil.getXMLHttpUrl(csTransUrl), callBack || !xmlHttp);
4012      request.setRequestHeader("Content-Type","application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
4013      request.send(MVUtil.getXMLHttpReq(csTransUrl, params)) ;
4014    } catch (e) 
4015    {
4016      MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.transformGeom", "MAPVIEWER-05511", e, this.errorHandler) ;
4017      return ;
4018    } 
4019   
4020    if (!callBack && xmlHttp)
4021    {
4022      if(request.status == 200)
4023      { 
4024        return transformed() ;
4025      }
4026    }
4027  }

4030   @returns The current map srid.
4031   @type    int
4032  */
4033  MVMapView.prototype.getSrid = function ()
4034  {
4035    return this.srid;
4036  }

4066  /**
4067  *This method sends a map request corresponding to the current map view to the MapViewer 
4068   server and gets the map image URL back from the server.  
4069  *@param {Function} callBack the user defined function that is called when the server 
4070                returns the map image URL. The map image URL is passed as the only 
4071                parameter to this function.
4072  *@param {String} format the map image format.
4073  *@param {int} width the width of the map image. If omitted, the map image width 
4074                will be set to the width of the current map div container.
4075  *@param {int} height the height of the map image. If omitted, the map image 
4076                height will be set to the height of the current map div container.
4077  *@returns none
4078  *@type void
4079  */
4080  MVMapView.prototype.getMapImageURL=function(callBack, format, width, height)
4081  {
4082    var xmlRequest = this.getMapAsXML(format, width, height) ;
4083    var localDomain = (this.baseURL == this.cfgbaseURL) ;
4084    var xmlHttp = localDomain || MVMapView.XMLHTTPEnabled ;
4085    var url="";
4086    if (MVMapView.XMLHTTPEnabled && !localDomain)
4087      url = this.cfgbaseURL ;
4088    else
4089      url = this.baseURL ;
4090    if (MVUtil.strEndWith(url, '/'))
4091      url = url + 'omserver'; 
4092    else
4093      url  = url + '/omserver';
4094         
4095    var req=MVUtil.getXMLHttpRequest(xmlHttp);
4096    req.open("POST", MVUtil.getXMLHttpUrl(url), true);
4097    req.setRequestHeader("Content-Type","application/x-www-form-urlencoded"); 
4098    req.send(MVUtil.getXMLHttpReq(url, "xml_request="+encodeURIComponent(xmlRequest)));
4099    
4100    var mv = this ;
4101    req.onreadystatechange = function() 
4102    {
4103      if (req.readyState == 4) 
4104      {
4105        if (req.status == 200) 
4106        {
4107          var content=req.responseText;
4108          var idx = content.indexOf("url=\"");
4109          if(idx<0)
4110          {
4111            MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.getMapImageURL", "MAPVIEWER-05519", content, mv.errorHandler) ;
4112            return ;
4113          }
4114          var result = content.substring(idx+5, content.indexOf("\"", idx+5)) ; 
4115          callBack(result) ;
4116        }
4117      }
4118    }
4119  }
4120  
4121  /**
4122  *This method returns the XML map request for the current map. The xml map request 
4123  *can be used to render the current map as a single map image.
4124  *@param {String} format the map image format.
4125  *@param {int} width the width of the map image. If omitted, the map image width 
4126                will be set to the width of the current map div container.
4127  *@param {int} height the height of the map image. If omitted, the map image 
4128                height will be set to the height of the current map div container.
4129  *@returns {String} the XML map request string.
4130  */
4131  MVMapView.prototype.getMapAsXML=function(format, width, height)
4132  {
4133    if(!width)
4134      width = this.getPaneWidth() ;
4135    if(!height)
4136      height = this.getPaneHeight() ;
4137    var xmlRequest="<?xml version=\"1.0\" standalone=\"yes\"?>"
4138    var ds = this.defaultDataSource ? this.defaultDataSource : MVMessages["default_datasource"] ;
4139    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+"<map_request datasource=\""+ds+"\" format=\""+format+"\" width=\""+
4140                          width+"\" height=\""+height+"\" antialiase=\"true\" "+
4141                          (this.getSrid()?"srid=\""+this.getSrid()+"\"":"");
4142    var externalAPITileLayerURL = null;
4143    for(i = 0; i < this.mapLayers.length; i++)
4144    {
4145      var tmpLayer = this.mapLayers[i];
4146      if(tmpLayer instanceof MVBingTileLayer)
4147        externalAPITileLayerURL = tmpLayer.getStaticMapURL();
4148      if(tmpLayer instanceof MVGoogleTileLayer)
4149        externalAPITileLayerURL = tmpLayer.getStaticMapURL();
4150    }
4151    if(externalAPITileLayerURL != null)
4152      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " bgimage=\"" + externalAPITileLayerURL +"\"";
4153    var copyright = this.getCopyright() ;
4154    if(copyright)
4155      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " footnote=\"" + copyright +"\"";
4156    xmlRequest = xmlRequest + ">"
4157    var size=parseInt(this.getPaneHeight())/this.pixPerY;
4158    var centerPoint=this.getCenter();
4159    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+"<center size=\""+size+"\"><geoFeature><geometricProperty typeName=\"center\"><Point><coordinates>"+centerPoint.sdo_point.x+","+centerPoint.sdo_point.y+"</coordinates></Point></geometricProperty></geoFeature></center>";
4160    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+"<themes>";
4161    for(i=0; i<this.mapLayers.length; i++)
4162    {
4163      if(this.mapLayers[i].isVisible() && this.mapLayers[i].layerControl && 
4164         !(this.mapLayers[i] instanceof MVCustomMapTileLayer))
4165        xmlRequest=xmlRequest+"<theme name=\"cached_basemap"+i+"\">"+this.mapLayers[i].layerControl.getXMLForPrint()+"</theme>";
4166    }
4167    var themesStr = "" ;
4168    var stylesStr = "" ;
4169    var nsdpStr = "" ;
4170    for(var i=0;i<this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length;i++)
4171    {
4172      if(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].isVisible())
4173      {
4174        var styleName = null;
4175        if (this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.customedMarker)
4176        {
4177          styleName = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.theme+"_markerstyle"
4178          var markerStyle = new MVStyleMarker(styleName,"image");
4179          var marker = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.customedMarker;
4180          markerStyle.setImageUrl(marker.imgURL)
4181          markerStyle.setSize(marker.width,marker.height);
4182          stylesStr += markerStyle.getXMLString();
4183        }
4184        themesStr += this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].beforePrint(styleName);
4185        if(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.nsdpObj!=null)
4186          nsdpStr += this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.nsdpObj.getXML(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi) ;
4187        var styles = this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].themebasedfoi.styles ;
4188        if(styles.length>0)
4189        {
4190          for(var j=0; j < styles.length; j++)
4191          {
4192            stylesStr += styles[j].getXMLString();
4193          }
4194        }
4195      }
4196    }
4197    for(var i=0;i<this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray.length;i++)
4198    {
4199      if (this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].style && 
4200          this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].style.getXMLString &&
4201          this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].visible)
4202        stylesStr += this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].style.getXMLString();
4203      if (this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].createMarker)
4204      {
4205        var styleName = "indfoi_"+this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].id+"_style";
4206        var markerStyle = new MVStyleMarker(styleName, "image");
4207        markerStyle.setImageUrl(this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].imgURL);
4208        markerStyle.setSize(this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].width, this.indFOIsControl.indFOIArray[i].height);
4209        stylesStr += markerStyle.getXMLString();
4210      }
4211    }
4212    
4213    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+themesStr+"</themes>";
4214    if(stylesStr!="")
4215      xmlRequest += " <styles>"+stylesStr+"</styles>" ;
4216    if(nsdpStr!="")
4217      xmlRequest += nsdpStr ;
4218    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+this.indFOIsControl.beforePrint();
4219    if(this.scalectl)
4220    {
4221      var position = "SOUTH_WEST";
4222      switch(this.scalebarPosition)
4223      {
4224        case 1: position = "NORTH_EAST";
4225                break;
4226        case 3: position = "SOUTH_EAST";
4227                break;
4228        case 4: position = "NORTH_WEST";
4229                break;
4230      }
4231      var mode = "DUAL_MODES";
4232      if (this.scalectl.format!=null && this.scalectl.format=="METRIC")
4233        mode = "METRIC_MODE";
4234      else if (this.scalectl.format!=null && this.scalectl.format=="IMPERIAL")
4235        mode = "US_MODE";
4236      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + "<scale_bar mode=\""+mode+"\" position=\"" + position + "\" ";
4237      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " color1=\"#000000\" color2=\"#FFFFFF\"";
4238      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " offset_x=\"" + this.scalebarOffsetWidth;
4239      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + "\" offset_y=\"" + this.scalebarOffsetHeight+"\"";
4240      if (this.scalectl.maxLength)
4241        xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " length_hint=\"" + this.scalectl.maxLength + "\"";
4242      if (this.msi.getCSType() == "PROJECTED" && this.scalectl.transformToGeodetic)
4243        xmlRequest = xmlRequest + " transform_to_wgs84=\"true\"";
4244      xmlRequest = xmlRequest + "/>";
4245    }
4246    xmlRequest=xmlRequest+"</map_request>";
4247    return xmlRequest;
4248  }

4252    return this.getMapAsXML("GIF_URL") ;

4283  /**
4284  *This method generates a printable map and prints it. The printable map must be 
4285  *placed inside a DIV element that is visible to printer but invisible on screen. 
4286  *The size and positioning of the printable map DIV can be customized.
4287  *@param {DIV} printMapDiv, a DIV element used to hold the printable map image.
4288  *@returns   None
4289  *@type void
4290  */
4291  MVMapView.prototype.print=function(printMapDiv)
4292  {
4293   var par = this;
4294   if(printMapDiv.style.position!="absolute")
4295     printMapDiv.style.position="relative";
4296   printMapDiv.style.width = MVUtil.pixel(this.getPaneWidth()) ;
4297   printMapDiv.style.height = MVUtil.pixel(this.getPaneHeight()) ;
4298   /*if (this.printImage)
4299   {
4300     window.print();
4301   }
4302   else */
4303   if(!this.printing)
4304   {
4305     this.printWaitStart();
4306     this.printReset();
4307     var xmlRequest=this.beforePrint();
4308     var localDomain = (this.baseURL == this.cfgbaseURL) ;
4309     var xmlHttp = localDomain || MVMapView.XMLHTTPEnabled ;
4310     var url="";
4311     if (MVMapView.XMLHTTPEnabled && !localDomain)
4312       url = this.cfgbaseURL ;
4313     else
4314       url = this.baseURL ;
4315     if (MVUtil.strEndWith(url, '/'))
4316       url = url + 'omserver'; 
4317     else
4318       url  = url + '/omserver';
4319         
4320     req=MVUtil.getXMLHttpRequest(xmlHttp);
4321     
4322     req.open("POST", MVUtil.getXMLHttpUrl(url), true);
4323     req.setRequestHeader("Content-Type","application/x-www-form-urlencoded"); 
4324     req.send(MVUtil.getXMLHttpReq(url, "xml_request="+encodeURIComponent(xmlRequest)));
4325     
4326     req.onreadystatechange = function() 
4327     {
4328       if (req.readyState == 4) 
4329       {
4330         if (req.status == 200) 
4331         {
4332           par.printDiv=printMapDiv;
4333           var img=document.createElement("img");
4334           var content=req.responseText;
4335           var idx = content.indexOf("url=\"");
4336           if(idx<0)
4337           {
4338             MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.print", "MAPVIEWER-05519", content, par.errorHandler) ;
4339             return ;
4340           }
4341           img.src=content.substring(idx+5, content.indexOf("\"", idx+5)) ; // content.getAttribute("url");
4342           img.style.position="absolute" ;
4343           img.style.left=MVUtil.pixel(0);
4344           img.style.top=MVUtil.pixel(0);
4345           //img.className="printimage";
4346           par.printDiv.appendChild(img);
4347           
4348           img.onload = MVUtil.closureWrapper(img,function()
4349           {
4350             par.printPrepare();
4351             if (par.mapDecorationArray!=null)
4352               for(var i=0;i<par.mapDecorationArray.length;i++)
4353               {
4354                 if (par.mapDecorationArray[i].isPrintable && par.mapDecorationArray[i].visible && !par.mapDecorationArray[i].collapsed)
4355                   par.printDiv.appendChild(par.mapDecorationArray[i].getPrintContainer());
4356               }
4357             //par.addPrintCopyRightPanel(true);
4358             par.printWaitEnd();
4359             window.print();
4360             par.printing=false;
4361           })
4362           par.printImage=img;
4363         }
4364       }
4365     }
4366 
4367    }
4368  }

4404  /**
4405  @private
4406  */
4407  MVMapView.prototype.addEventHandlers = function()
4408  {
4409    var this_map = this;
4410    var browser = this.getBrowserType();
4411    this.real_base_div.tabIndex = 0;
4412    this.real_base_div.onfocus = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4413    {
4414        this_map.enableMapEventListner=true;
4415    });
4416    
4417    this.real_base_div.onblur = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4418    {
4419        this_map.enableMapEventListner=false;
4420    });
4421 
4422    this.base_div.onmouseover = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4423      {
4424        this_map.enableMapEventListner=true;
4425      });
4426    
4427    this.base_div.onmouseout = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function(evt)
4428    {
4429      evt = (evt) ? evt : ((window.event) ? event : null);
4430      var clientx=evt.clientX;
4431      var clienty=evt.clientY;
4432 
4433      var width = this_map.getPaneWidth();
4434      var height = this_map.getPaneHeight();
4435      
4436      var inMapXY = this_map.getEventCoords(evt) ;
4437      
4438      if(inMapXY.left<=0 || inMapXY.left>=width || 
4439         inMapXY.top<=0 || inMapXY.top>=height ||
4440         clientx<=1 || clientx>=document.body.clientWidth ||
4441         clienty<=1 || clienty>=document.body.clientHeight)
4442      {    
4443       this_map.mUp( evt );
4444       this_map.enableMapEventListner=false;
4445       if (this_map.arrowKeys.contains(37)) this_map.arrowKeys.remove(37);
4446       if (this_map.arrowKeys.contains(38)) this_map.arrowKeys.remove(38);
4447       if (this_map.arrowKeys.contains(39)) this_map.arrowKeys.remove(39);
4448       if (this_map.arrowKeys.contains(40)) this_map.arrowKeys.remove(40);                   
4449      }
4450    });
4451      
4452    this.base_div.onclick = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function(evt)
4453    {
4454     if((this_map.mouseDownLoc && this_map.mouseUpLoc &&
4455        (Math.abs(this_map.mouseDownLoc.left-this_map.mouseUpLoc.left) > 1 ||
4456         Math.abs(this_map.mouseUpLoc.top-this_map.mouseUpLoc.top) > 1)) ||
4457         (Math.abs(this_map.mouseDownScreenX-this_map.mouseUpScreenX) > 1 ||
4458         Math.abs(this_map.mouseDownScreenY-this_map.mouseUpScreenY) > 1))
4459       return ;
4460     if (this_map.mouseclickListener)
4461     {
4462       this_map.mouseclickListener(MVUtil.getEvent(evt));
4463     }
4464     MVUtil.runListeners(this_map.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_CLICK,[MVUtil.getEvent(evt)]);
4465    });
4466    
4467    if(!this.origBodyOnmousedownListener)
4468     MVUtil.detachEvent(document.body, "mousedown", this.origBodyOnmousedownListener) ;
4469    this.origBodyOnmousedownListener = MVUtil.closureWrapper(document.body, function()
4470    {
4471      this_map.enableMapEventListner=false;
4472    });   
4473    MVUtil.attachEvent(document.body, "mousedown", this.origBodyOnmousedownListener) ;
4474    
4475    if ( browser == "IF" )
4476    {
4477      this.base_div.onselectstart = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4478      {
4479        if ((this_map.infoLayer && this_map.infoLayer.mouseOnInfoWindow) ||
4480             (this_map.infoLayer2 && this_map.infoLayer2.mouseOnInfoWindow))
4481          return true;
4482        else
4483          return false;
4484      });
4485      this.base_div.oncontextmenu = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function(evt)
4486      {
4487        this_map.getMPos(window.event);
4488        if (this_map.rightclickListener)
4489        {
4490          this_map.rightclickListener(MVUtil.getEvent(evt));
4491        }
4492        MVUtil.runListeners(this_map.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_RIGHT_CLICK,[MVUtil.getEvent(evt)]);
4493        if ((this_map.infoLayer && this_map.infoLayer.mouseOnInfoWindow))
4494          return true;
4495        else
4496          return false;
4497      });
4498      
4499      if(this.mouseWheelZoomEnabled)
4500        this.base_div.onmousewheel = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4501        {
4502          return this_map._mouseWheel( window.event );
4503        });
4504      else
4505        this.base_div.onmousewheel = null;
4506     
4507      this.base_div.onmousedown = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4508      {
4509        MVUtil.stopEvent(window.event);
4510        return this_map.mDn( window.event );
4511      });
4512      
4513      this.base_div.onmousemove = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4514      {
4515        return this_map.mMv( window.event );
4516      });
4517     
4518      this.base_div.onmouseup = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4519      {
4520        this_map.enableMapEventListner=true;
4521        MVUtil.runListeners(this_map.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_UP, [window.event]);
4522        return this_map.mUp( window.event );
4523      });
4524     
4525      this.base_div.ondblclick = MVUtil.closureWrapper(this.base_div, function()
4526      {
4527        return this_map.mDbClick( window.event );
4528      });
4529      
4530      document.body.attachEvent('onmouseup', MVUtil.closureWrapper(document.body, function()
4531      {
4532        return this_map.mUp(window.event);
4533      }));
4534 
4535      /*if(window.parent && window.parent.window)
4536      {
4537       window.parent.window.document.body.attachEvent('onmouseup', MVUtil.closureWrapper(window.parent.window.document.body, function()
4538       {
4539         return this_map.mUp(window.event);
4540       }));
4541      }*/
4542 
4543      if (!this.overview)
4544      {
4545        if(!this.origBodyOnkeydownListener)
4546         MVUtil.detachEvent(document.body, "keydown", this.origBodyOnkeydownListener) ;
4547        this.origBodyOnkeydownListener = MVUtil.closureWrapper(document.body, function()
4548        {
4549          return this_map._keyDown( window.event );
4550        });
4551        MVUtil.attachEvent(document.body, "keydown", this.origBodyOnkeydownListener) ;
4552     
4553        if(!this.origBodyOnkeyupListener)
4554         MVUtil.detachEvent(document.body, "keyup", this.origBodyOnkeyupListener) ;
4555        this.origBodyOnkeyupListener = MVUtil.closureWrapper(document.body, function()
4556        {
4557          return this_map._keyUp( window.event );
4558        });
4559        MVUtil.attachEvent(document.body, "keyup", this.origBodyOnkeyupListener) ;
4560        
4561        var realResize = function()
4562        {
4563          this_map._mapResized( window.event );
4564          /*if (this_map.overviewmap)
4565          {

4922        {
4923          _event.preventDefault() ;
4924          this_map.cancelTouchAndHold() ;
4925          if(this_map.touchCount==2)
4926          {
4927            this_map.touchMove(_event) ;
4928            var scale = this_map.pinchZoomScale ;
4929            if(!this_map.shouldPinchZoom(scale))
4930              return ;
4931            this_map.pinchZooming = true ;
4932            for(var i=0; i< this_map.mapLayers.length; i++)
4933            {
4934              if(this_map.mapLayers[i].layerControl)
4935              {
4936                this_map.mapLayers[i].layerControl.zoomControl.scaleTiles(scale);
4937              }
4938            }
4939            return ;
4940          }
4941          return this_map.mMv( _event );
4942        }, true);
4943     
4944      MVUtil.setListener(this.base_div, "touchend", function( _event )
4945        {
4946          _event.preventDefault() ;
4947          this_map.enableMapEventListner=true;
4948          
4949          this_map.touchEnd(_event) ; 
4950          if(this_map.touchCount>0)
4951            return ;
4952          
4953          var scale = this_map.pinchZoomScale ;
4954          if(this_map.pinchZooming)
4955          {
4956            var zl = this_map.getPinchZoomingLevel(scale) ;           
4957            this_map.zoomTo(zl, null, true, true);
4958            this_map.pinchZoomScale = 1 ;
4959            this_map.pinchZooming = false ;
4960          }
4961          else
4962          {
4963            var lastTouchLoc = this_map.lastTouchLoc ;
4964            var touchLoc = MVUtil.getMouseXY(_event) ;
4965            this_map.lastTouchLoc = touchLoc ;
4966            var lastTouch = this_map.lastTouch ; 
4967            var thisTouch = (new Date()).getTime();
4968            this_map.lastTouch = thisTouch ;
4969            if(thisTouch - lastTouch < 500 && lastTouchLoc && 
4970               Math.abs(lastTouchLoc.x-touchLoc.x)<=10 && Math.abs(lastTouchLoc.y-touchLoc.y)<=10) // 500 ms is double touch
4971            {
4972              this_map.mDbClick( _event );
4973            }
4974            else
4975            {
4976              this_map.mUp( _event );
4977            }
4978          }
4979        }, true);
4980      
4981    }
4982  }

4987  MVMapView.prototype._mouseWheel = function( _event )
4988  {
4989    if ( _event.wheelDelta > 0 ) this.zoomIn();
4990    else this.zoomOut();
4991    return false;
4992  }

4994  /**
4995  @private
4996  */
4997  MVMapView.prototype._mapResized = function( _event )
4998  { 
4999    this.sizeChanging = false ;
5000    /*this.oldPaneWidth = null ;
5001    this.oldPaneHeight = null ;*/
5002    this.zoomLevel = this.getZoomLevel();
5003    if (this.zoomLevel > this.maxZoom )
5004    {
5005       this.zoomLevel = this.maxZoom ;
5006       return ;
5007    }
5008    MVUtil.setLeftTop(this.div, 0, 0);
5009    MVUtil.setLeftTop(this.info_div, 0, 0);
5010    this.divLeft = 0;
5011    this.divTop  = 0;
5012    this.origLeft = this.divLeft;
5013    this.origTop = this.divTop;
5014    this.dragOffsetX = 0;
5015    this.dragOffsetY = 0; 
5016    this.setZoomLevel(this.zoomLevel);  
5017    if (this.center_mark)
5018    {
5019      if(this.centerMarkUrl)
5020         this.setCenterMark(this.centerMarkUrl, this.centerMarkW, this.centerMarkH);
5021      else
5022         this.setCenterMark(MVGlobalVariables.imgFilePath + "center.gif", 20, 20);
5023    }
5024    if (this.navigationPanel)
5025      this.navigationPanel.init(null, this);
5026    //this.setCenter(this.mapCenterX, this.mapCenterY);  
5027    this.display();
5028    if (this.scalectl)
5029    {
5030       this.scalectl.update(this);
5031    }
5032    if (this.overviewmap)
5033    {
5034      this.overviewmap.submap._mapResized(); 
5035      this.overviewmap.resetRectangle();
5036    }
5037    if (this.mapDecorationArray != null)
5038      for (var i=0;i<this.mapDecorationArray.length;i++)
5039      {
5040        //if (!this.mapDecorationArray[i].collapsible)
5041          //this.mapDecorationArray[i].initPosition(this.mapDecorationArray[i].fixedDiv);
5042        this.mapDecorationArray[i].refreshPosition();
5043      }
5044    return false;
5045  }

5056  /**
5057  * This methods enables or disables keyboard panning. When keyboard panning is
5058  * enabled, user can pan the map by pressing the arrow keys.
5059  *@param {Boolean} enable a Boolean that specifies whether to enable keyboard panning,
5060                    true(enable) or false(disable).
5061  */
5062  MVMapView.prototype.enableKeyboardPanning = function(enable)
5063  {
5064    this.keyboardPanningEnabled = enable ;
5065  }
5066  /**
5067  @private
5068  */
5069  MVMapView.prototype._keyDown = function(_event)
5070  {
5071    //MVi18n.reportError(this.keyboardPanningEnabled);
5072    if(!this.enableMapEventListner || !this.keyboardPanningEnabled) 
5073      return true;
5074    if ( this.scroll_left == undefined || this.scroll_up == undefined || this.scroll_right == undefined || this.scroll_down == undefined )
5075    {
5076      this.scroll_left = 0;
5077      this.scroll_up = 0;
5078      this.scroll_right = 0;
5079      this.scroll_down = 0;
5080      this.scroll_distance = 0;
5081    }
5082    var numcode_offset = (this.getBrowserType() != "OS") ? 96 : 48;
5083    if (!_event.shiftKey)
5084    {
5085      if(_event.ctrlKey)
5086      {
5087         switch (_event.keyCode)
5088         {
5089            case 90: //88 ctrl+z
5090                     for (var i=0;i < this.mapDecorationArray.length; i++)
5091                       if (this.mapDecorationArray[i].collapsible)
5092                         this.mapDecorationArray[i].startScrollElement();
5093                     break;
5094         }
5095         return true ;
5096      }
5097      switch (_event.keyCode)
5098      {
5099        case 37: this.scroll_left = 1; this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Left
5100        break;
5101        case 38: this.scroll_up = 1; this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Up
5102        break;
5103        case 39: this.scroll_right = 1; this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Right
5104        break;
5105        case 40: this.scroll_down = 1; this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Down
5106        break;
5107        case numcode_offset + 1: this.scroll_left = 1;//97 or 49 (NumPad) 1 or 1
5108                                 this.scroll_down = 1;
5109        break;
5110        case numcode_offset + 2: this.scroll_down = 1;//98 or 50 (NumPad) 2 or 2
5111                                 this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);
5112        break;
5113        case numcode_offset + 3: this.scroll_right = 1;//99 or 51 (NumPad) 3 or 3
5114                                 this.scroll_down = 1;
5115        break;
5116        case numcode_offset + 4: this.scroll_left = 1; //100 or 52 (NumPad) 4 or 4
5117                                 this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);
5118        break;
5119        case numcode_offset + 5:                       //101 or 53 (NumPad) 5 or 5 do nothing
5120        break; 
5121        case numcode_offset + 6: this.scroll_right = 1;//102 or 54 (NumPad) 6 or 6
5122                                 this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);
5123        break;
5124        case numcode_offset + 7: this.scroll_left = 1; //103 or 55 (NumPad) 7 or 7
5125                                 this.scroll_up = 1;
5126        break;
5127        case numcode_offset + 8: this.scroll_up = 1;   //104 or 56 (NumPad) 8 or 8
5128                                 this.arrowKeys.add(_event.keyCode);
5129        break;
5130        case numcode_offset + 9: this.scroll_up = 1;   //105 or 57 (NumPad) 9 or 9
5131                                 this.scroll_right = 1;
5132        break;
5133        default: return true;
5134      }
5135      //this.scroll_distance = 150;
5136      //this.smoothScroll( ( this.scroll_right - this.scroll_left ) * this.scroll_distance, ( this.scroll_down - this.scroll_up ) * this.scroll_distance );
5137      this.startArrowScroll();
5138      return false ;
5139    }
5140    else
5141     return true ;
5142   }
5143   
5144  /**
5145  @private
5146  */
5147  MVMapView.prototype._keyUp = function( _event )
5148  { 
5149    if(!this.enableMapEventListner) return;
5150    var numcode_offset = ( this.getBrowserType() != "OS" ) ? 96 : 48;
5151    if (_event.shiftKey)
5152    {
5153      switch (_event.keyCode)
5154      {
5155        case 37: this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5156                 //Arrow Left
5157        break;
5158        case 38: this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Up
5159        break;
5160        case 39: this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Right
5161                 
5162        break;
5163        case 40: this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Down
5164        break;
5165        default: return true;
5166      }
5167    }
5168    else
5169    {
5170      switch (_event.keyCode)
5171      {
5172        case 33: this.smoothScroll( 0, - this.getPaneHeight() / 2 );//Page Up
5173        break;
5174        case 34: this.smoothScroll( 0, this.getPaneHeight() / 2 );//Page Down
5175        break;
5176        case 35: this.smoothScroll( this.getPaneWidth() / 2, 0 );//End
5177        break;
5178        case 36: this.smoothScroll( - this.getPaneWidth() / 2, 0 );//Home
5179        break;
5180        case 37: //this.scroll_left = 0; 
5181                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);//Arrow Left
5182         //this.smoothScroll( - this.getPaneWidth() / 2, 0 );
5183        break;
5184        case 38: //this.scroll_up = 0; 
5185                 this.arrowKeys.remove( _event.keyCode);//Arrow Up
5186 
5187        break;
5188        case 39: //this.scroll_right = 0; 
5189                 this.arrowKeys.remove( _event.keyCode);//Arrow Right
5190 
5191        break;
5192        case 40: //this.scroll_down = 0; 
5193                 this.arrowKeys.remove( _event.keyCode);//Arrow Down
5194        break;
5195        case numcode_offset + 1: this.scroll_left = 0;
5196                                 this.scroll_down = 0;                               
5197        break;
5198        case numcode_offset + 2: this.scroll_down = 0;
5199                                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5200        break;
5201        case numcode_offset + 3: this.scroll_right = 0;
5202                                 this.scroll_down = 0;
5203        break;
5204        case numcode_offset + 4: this.scroll_left = 0;
5205                                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5206        break;
5207        case numcode_offset + 5: this.scroll_left = 0;
5208                                 this.scroll_up = 0;
5209                                 this.scroll_right = 0;
5210                                 this.scroll_down = 0;
5211        break;
5212        case numcode_offset + 6: this.scroll_right = 0;
5213                                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5214        break;
5215        case numcode_offset + 7: this.scroll_left = 0;
5216                                 this.scroll_up = 0;
5217        break;
5218        case numcode_offset + 8: this.scroll_up = 0;
5219                                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5220        break;
5221        case numcode_offset + 9: this.scroll_up = 0;
5222                                 this.arrowKeys.remove(_event.keyCode);
5223        this.scroll_right = 0;
5224        break;
5225        case 107:                this.zoomIn();  //(NumPad) +  
5226        break;
5227        case 187:                this.zoomIn(); //+
5228        break;
5229        case 109:                this.zoomOut();  //(NumPad) - or -
5230        break;
5231        case 189:                this.zoomOut(); //-
5232        break;
5233        case 61:                 this.zoomIn(); 
5234        break;
5235        case 43:                 this.zoomIn(); 
5236        break;
5237        case 45:                 this.zoomOut(); 
5238        break;
5239        case 95:                 this.zoomOut(); 
5240        break;
5241        default: return true;
5242      }//end switch 
5243     /*
5244     switch ( _event.which )
5245     {
5246       case 61:  this.zoomIn();
5247        break;
5248       case 43:  this.zoomIn();
5249       break;
5250       case 45:  this.zoomOut();
5251       break;
5252       case 95:  this.zoomOut();
5253       break;
5254       default: return true;
5255     }*/
5256   }//end else
5257   return false;
5258  }

5280  /**@private
5281   * Get the mouse event location relative to the map container's upper left corner.
5282  */
5283  MVMapView.prototype.getEventCoords = function (evt) 
5284  {
5285    var coords = {left:0, top:0};
5286    absolutePosition = MVUtil.offsetPositionAbsolute(this.real_base_div) ;
5287    var mouseLoc = MVUtil.getMouseXY(evt) ;
5288    coords.left = mouseLoc.x - absolutePosition.x;
5289    coords.top = mouseLoc.y - absolutePosition.y;
5290    return coords;
5291  }

5293  /**
5294  @private
5295  */
5296  MVMapView.prototype.mDn = function (evt)
5297  {
5298    evt = (evt) ? evt : ((window.event) ? event : null);
5299    var Coords = this.getEventCoords(evt);
5300    var mouseLoc = MVUtil.getMouseXY(evt) ;
5301    
5302    this.mouseDownScreenX = mouseLoc.x;
5303    this.mouseDownScreenY = mouseLoc.y;
5304    this.mouseDownLoc = Coords ;   
5305    
5306    if(this.marqueeZoomOn && this.marqueeRectDone)
5307    {
5308      this.clearMarqueeRect = true ;
5309      //return ;
5310    }
5311    
5312    MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners, MVEvent.MOUSE_DOWN, [evt]);
5313    
5314    if (this.mapmoveflag == false)  return;
5315    
5316    if (!MVUtil.mouseLeftKeyPressed(evt))
5317    {
5318      return;
5319    }
5320    /*if (!this.mapLockMode && ((MVGlobalVariables.browser=="IF" && evt.button==1) || 
5321        (MVGlobalVariables.browser !="IF" && evt.button==0))) 
5322      MVUtil.setCursor(this.base_div,this.cursorStyleDragging);*/
5323    if ((MVGlobalVariables.browser !="SF") && (MVGlobalVariables.browser.indexOf("OS") !=0) && 
5324        ((MVGlobalVariables.browser=="IF" && evt.button==4) || (MVGlobalVariables.browser !="IF"
5325         && evt.button==1)))
5326    {
5327      //evt.cancelBubble=true;
5328      //evt.returnValue=false;
5329      MVUtil.stopEvent(evt);
5330      return false;
5331    }
5332    for (var i = 0; i < this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup.length; i++)
5333    {
5334      if(this.ThemeBasedFOIGroup[i].isLoading())
5335      {
5336         this.setTileLayerCursor("wait");
5337      }
5338    }
5339    if ((MVGlobalVariables.browser.indexOf("OS")==0) && evt.button==2)
5340    {
5341      mouseRightClick();
5342    }
5343    if (this.m_scroll_id !=null)
5344    {
5345      clearInterval(this.m_scroll_id);
5346      this.m_scroll_id=null;
5347    }
5348    this.curLay=this;
5349    
5350    this.setDragOffset(Coords.left, Coords.top);
5351    this.dragCoords = this.getEventCoords(evt);
5352    this.getMPos(evt);
5353    if( MVGlobalVariables.browserClass==2 ) evt.returnValue=false;
5354    if( this.mapLockMode ) this.curLay=null;
5355    this.fetchMapOnDrag();
5356    this.divLeftOrig = MVUtil.getLeft(this.div);
5357    this.mapWindowMinXOrig = this.mapWindowMinLon ;
5358    this.mapWindowMaxYOrig = this.mapWindowMaxLon ;
5359    this.mapCenterXOrig = this.mapCenterX ;
5360    return false;
5361  }

5399  */
5400  MVMapView.prototype.stopDragging = function()
5401  {
5402    if(this.draggedMapDecoration)
5403    {
5404     this.draggedMapDecoration.stopDragging(); 
5405    }
5406    if(this.marqueeZoomOn && this.clearMarqueeRect)
5407    {
5408      this.marqueeZoomRectangleTool.clear() ;
5409      this.marqueeZoom() ;
5410      //return ;
5411    }
5412    this.curLay = null ;
5413    this.setTileLayerCursor(this.cursorStyleDefault);
5414    this.beingDragged=false;
5415    /*
5416    For IE, if a node is removed from dom tree, the attribute of parentNode is not null, it's "#document-fragment"
5417    */
5418    if (this.transparentLayer.parentNode == null || (MVGlobalVariables.browser=="IF" && this.transparentLayer.parentNode.tagName!="DIV"))
5419      this.div.appendChild(this.transparentLayer) ;
5420  }

5422  /**
5423  @private
5424  */
5425  MVMapView.prototype.mMv = function(evt)
5426  {   
5427    this.getMPos(MVUtil.getEvent(evt));
5428 
5429    if(this.draggedMapDecoration)
5430    {
5431      MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_MOVE,[evt]);
5432      var mouseLoc = MVUtil.getMouseXY(evt);
5433      //document.getElementById("message").innerHTML += mouseLoc +"<br>";
5434      this.draggedMapDecoration.setLeftTop(
5435        this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartLeft+(mouseLoc.x-this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartMouseLoc.x), 
5436        this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartTop+(mouseLoc.y-this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartMouseLoc.y)) ;
5437      /*MVUtil.setLeftTop(this.draggedMapDecoration.contentdiv, 
5438                        this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartLeft+(mouseLoc.x-this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartMouseLoc.x), 
5439                        this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartTop+(mouseLoc.y-this.draggedMapDecoration.dragStartMouseLoc.y));*/
5440      if(this.draggedMapDecoration.dragListener)
5441        this.draggedMapDecoration.dragListener(this.draggedMapDecoration.getPosition());
5442 	 MVUtil.runListeners(this.draggedMapDecoration.EventListeners,MVEvent.DRAG,[this.draggedMapDecoration.getPosition()]);
5443      return ;
5444    }
5445    if (this.mapmoveflag == false || 
5446        !this.curLay || this.mapLockMode || !this.draggingEnabled)  
5447    {
5448      // fire mouse move listener when map is not dragged.
5449      MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_MOVE,[evt]);
5450      return;
5451    }
5452    
5453    if(!this.beingDragged)
5454    {
5455      this.beingDragged=true;
5456      this.div.removeChild(this.transparentLayer) ;
5457    }
5458    /*else if(MVGlobalVariables.browser == "IF" && evt.button!=1)
5459    {
5460      this.setTileLayerCursor(this.cursorStyleDefault);
5461      this.mUp(evt) ;
5462      return ;
5463    }*/
5464    
5465    this.printReset();
5466    var Coords = this.getEventCoords(evt);
5467    if(this.currentCursor!=this.cursorStyleDragging)
5468    {
5469      this.setTileLayerCursor(this.cursorStyleDragging);
5470      this.currentCursor = this.cursorStyleDragging ;
5471    }
5472    
5473    if(this.marqueeZoomOn && this.marqueeRectDone && this.clearMarqueeRect)
5474       this.clearMarqueeRect = false ;
5475    
5476    this.move(Coords.left, Coords.top);
5477    this.dragCoords = Coords ;
5478 
5479    if (this.overviewmap)
5480    {
5481      this.overviewmap.moveRectanglefromMainMap(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop)
5482    }
5483    if (this.movingListener)
5484    {
5485      this.movingListener(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop);
5486    }
5487    return false;
5488  }

5490  /**
5491  @private
5492  */
5493  MVMapView.prototype.mUp = function (evt)
5494  {
5495    evt = (evt) ? evt : ((window.event) ? event : null); 
5496    /*var Coords = this.getEventCoords(evt);
5497    this.mouseUpLoc = Coords ;   */
5498    this.mouseUpLoc = this.dragCoords ;
5499    var mouseLoc = MVUtil.getMouseXY(evt) ;
5500    this.mouseUpScreenX = mouseLoc.x;
5501    this.mouseUpScreenY = mouseLoc.y;
5502    if (this.mapmoveflag == false)  return;
5503    this.setTileLayerCursor(this.cursorStyleDefault);
5504    this.currentCursor = this.cursorStyleDefault ;
5505    if(!this.curLay && !this.mapLockMode) return;
5506    this.stopDragging() ;
5507    //if(evt) this.getMPos(evt); 
5508    if(this.dragCoords) 
5509    {
5510     this.getMPos(this.dragCoords);  
5511     this.dragCoords = null ;
5512    }
5513    else
5514    {
5515     this.getMPos(evt);
5516    }
5517    
5518    this.do_GetMinMaxLonLat();
5519    if (this.scrolled == true)
5520    {
5521      for(var i=0; i<this.mapLayers.length; i++)
5522       this.mapLayers[i].scrollTiles();
5523      //this.infoLayer.scrollInfoLayer();
5524      this.scrollThemeBasedFOIs();
5525      this.scrolled = false;
5526      if (this.overviewmap)
5527      {
5528        this.overviewmap.refreshSubMap();
5529      }
5530      if (this.recenterListener)
5531      {
5532       this.recenterListener();
5533      }
5534      MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.RECENTER);
5535      if (this.scalectl)
5536      {
5537        this.scalectl.update(this);
5538      }
5539    }
5540    if (this.fetchingMapId != null)
5541    {
5542      clearTimeout( this.fetchingMapId);
5543    } 
5544    this.setExternalAPITileLayersCenter(this.mapCenterX, this.mapCenterY, this.zoomLevel, true);
5545    this.printReset();
5546  }

5548  /**
5549  This method will choose whether to recenter or zoomin when the user doubleclicks the mouse on map
5550  @param {String} action it specified the action when the user doubleclicks the mouse on map.If it equals "recenter" the map will move and change the center to the clicked point
5551  If it equals "zoomin",the map will zoom in. The  default value is "recenter"
5552  */
5553  MVMapView.prototype.setDoubleClickAction = function(action)
5554  {
5555    if (action==null || (action!='recenter' && action !='zoomin') )
5556    {
5557      MVi18n.reportError("MVMapView.setDoubleClickAction", "MAPVIEWER-05519", "action", this.errorHandler);
5558      return ;
5559    }
5560    this.doubleClickAction=action;
5561  }
5562  
5563  /**
5564  @private
5565  */
5566  MVMapView.prototype.mDbClick = function(evt)
5567  {
5568    evt=(evt) ? evt : ((window.event) ? event : null);
5569    if( (this.EventListeners[MVEvent.MOUSE_DOUBLE_CLICK]!=null && this.EventListeners[MVEvent.MOUSE_DOUBLE_CLICK].length != 0 ) || this.dblclickListener)
5570    {
5571        if (this.dblclickListener){
5572          this.dblclickListener(MVUtil.getEvent(evt));
5573        }
5574        MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.MOUSE_DOUBLE_CLICK,[MVUtil.getEvent(evt)]);
5575        return true;
5576    }
5577    if (!this.overview && this.doubleClickAction=="zoomin")
5578    {
5579      this.zoomIn(this.getMouseLocation());
5580      return true;
5581    }
5582    if( this.mapLockMode )
5583    {
5584      this.curLay=null;
5585      this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5586      return true;
5587    }
5588    this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5589    if (this.m_scroll_id !=null)
5590    {
5591      clearInterval(this.m_scroll_id);
5592      this.m_scroll_id=null;
5593    }
5594    var Coords = this.getEventCoords(evt);
5595    var mouseX = Coords.left;
5596    var mouseY = Coords.top;
5597    this.map_moveX = this.getPaneWidth()/2 - mouseX;
5598    this.map_moveY = this.getPaneHeight()/2 - mouseY;
5599          
5600    this.distance = Math.sqrt(this.map_moveX * this.map_moveX + this.map_moveY * this.map_moveY);
5601    this.stepTime = 20;
5602    this.panWidth = this.getPaneWidth();
5603    this.panHeight = this.getPaneHeight();
5604    this.totalTime = this.distance > ((this.panWidth + this.panHeight)/4)?300:200;
5605    this.loopCount = 0;
5606    this.curX = 0;
5607    this.curY = 0;
5608    this.smoothPan();   
5609  }
5610  
5611  /**
5612   * This methods pans the map. The panning offset is specified by screen pixels on 
5613   * vertical and horizontal directions.
5614   * @param {int} x the panning offset in pixels on horizontal direction. A positive value 
5615   *                pans the map to the right and a negative value pans the map to the left.
5616   * @param {int} y the panning offset in pixels on vertical direction. A positive value
5617   *                pans the map downward and a negative value pans the map upward.
5618   * @return none.
5619   * @type void
5620   */
5621  MVMapView.prototype.pan = function (x, y)
5622  {
5623    this.smoothScroll(x, y) ;
5624  }
5625  
5626  /**
5627  @private
5628  */
5629  MVMapView.prototype.smoothScroll = function (_x, _y)
5630  { 
5631    if (_x == 0 && _y == 0)
5632    {
5633      return;
5634    }
5635    if( this.mapLockMode )
5636    {
5637      this.curLay=null;
5638      this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5639      return true;
5640    }
5641    this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5642   
5643    if (this.m_scroll_id !=null)
5644    {
5645      clearTimeout(this.m_scroll_id);
5646      this.m_scroll_id=null;
5647    }
5648    this.map_moveX = _x * (-1);
5649    this.map_moveY = _y * (-1);
5650    this.distance = Math.sqrt(_x*_x+_y*_y);
5651    this.stepTime= 10;
5652    this.panWidth = this.getPaneWidth();
5653    this.panHeight = this.getPaneHeight();
5654    this.totalTime = this.distance > ((this.panWidth + this.panHeight)/4)?300:200;
5655    this.loopCount = 0;
5656    this.curX = 0;
5657    this.curY = 0;
5658    this.smoothPan(); 
5659  }
5660  
5661  /**
5662  @private
5663  */
5664  MVMapView.prototype.smoothPan = function(noSmoothPanning)
5665  {
5666    /* Do not check map_moveX and this.map_moveY at the beginning. Defer the 
5667     * checking so that the themes will be checked at least once.
5668     */
5669    /*if(this.map_moveX == 0 && this.map_moveY ==0)
5670       return;*/
5671    this.loopCount++;
5672    var t= noSmoothPanning?1:this.loopCount*this.stepTime/this.totalTime;
5673    this.targetX = this.map_moveX * (2*t-t*t);
5674    this.targetY = this.map_moveY * (2*t-t*t);   
5675    var t1= this.panWidth/2;
5676    var t2= this.panHeight/2;
5677    this.setDragOffset(t1,t2); 
5678    t1=Math.round(this.targetX-this.curX)+ this.panWidth/2;
5679    t2=Math.round(this.targetY-this.curY)+ this.panHeight/2;
5680    this.move(t1, t2);
5681    if (this.overviewmap)
5682    {
5683      this.overviewmap.moveRectanglefromMainMap(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop)
5684    }
5685    if (this.movingListener)
5686    {
5687      this.movingListener(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop);
5688    }
5689    this.curX = this.targetX;
5690    this.curY = this.targetY;
5691     
5692    this.do_GetMinMaxLonLat();
5693    for(i=0; i < this.mapLayers.length; i++)
5694        this.mapLayers[i].scrollTiles();
5695    if (t < 1.0 && !(this.map_moveX == 0 && this.map_moveY==0))
5696    {
5697      this.m_scroll_id = this.setTimeout("this.smoothPan()", this.stepTime);
5698      this.smoothPanning = true ;
5699    }  
5700    else
5701    {
5702      clearTimeout(this.m_scroll_id);
5703      this.m_scroll_id=null;
5704      //this.infoLayer.scrollInfoLayer();
5705      this.scrollThemeBasedFOIs() ;
5706      this.scrolled = false;
5707      if (this.overviewmap)
5708      {
5709        this.overviewmap.refreshSubMap();
5710      }
5711      if (this.recenterListener)
5712      {
5713        this.recenterListener();
5714      }
5715      MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.RECENTER);
5716      if (this.scalectl)
5717      {
5718        this.scalectl.update(this);
5719      }
5720      this.printReset();
5721      this.smoothPanning = false ;
5722      return false; 
5723    }
5724  }
5725  
5726  /**
5727  @private
5728  */
5729  MVMapView.prototype.smoothMove = function(x,y)
5730  {
5731    this.targetX = x*(-1);
5732    this.targetY = y*(-1);
5733    var t1= this.getPaneWidth()/2;
5734    var t2= this.getPaneHeight()/2;
5735    this.setDragOffset(t1,t2); 
5736    t1=Math.round(this.targetX+ this.getPaneWidth()/2);
5737    t2=Math.round(this.targetY+ this.getPaneHeight()/2);
5738    this.move(t1, t2);
5739    /*
5740    if (this.overviewmap)
5741    {
5742      this.overviewmap.moveRectanglefromMainMap(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop)
5743    }
5744    */
5745    if (this.movingListener)
5746    {
5747      this.movingListener(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop);
5748    }
5749    
5750    for(i=0; i < this.mapLayers.length; i++)
5751        this.mapLayers[i].scrollTiles();
5752  }

5756  /**
5757  @private
5758  */
5759  MVMapView.prototype.setTimeout=function(timeoutHandler,elapseTime)
5760  {
5761     var Ie="tempVar" + MV_timeoutCounter;
5762     MV_timeoutCounter++;
5763     eval(Ie+" = this;");
5764     // var oi=timeoutHandler.replace(/\\/g,"\\\\").replace(//g,'\"');
5765     // break a sinle statement with two replace calls into two statements 
5766     // for js obfuscator -- ji
5767     var oi=timeoutHandler.replace(/\\/g,"\\\\") ;
5768     oi = oi.replace(/\"/g,'\\"');
5769     return window.setTimeout(Ie+'._setTimeoutDispatcher("'+oi+'");'+Ie+" = null;",elapseTime);
5770  }

5791  /**
5792  @private
5793  */
5794  MVMapView.prototype.arrowScroll = function ()
5795  { 
5796    if( this.mapLockMode )
5797    {
5798      this.curLay=null;
5799      this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5800      return true;
5801    }
5802    this.base_div.style.cursor=this.cursorStyleDefault;
5803   
5804    if (this.m_scroll_id != null)
5805    {
5806      clearTimeout(this.m_scroll_id);
5807      this.m_scroll_id = null;
5808    }
5809    var num_offset = (this.getBrowserType() != "OS") ? 96 : 48;   
5810    if(this.arrowKeys.length > 0)
5811    {
5812      var a = ((this.arrowKeys.contains(37)|| this.arrowKeys.contains(num_offset + 4))?1:0) + 
5813              ((this.arrowKeys.contains(39)|| this.arrowKeys.contains(num_offset + 6))?-1:0);
5814      
5815      var b=((this.arrowKeys.contains(38) || this.arrowKeys.contains(num_offset + 8))? 1:0)+
5816            ((this.arrowKeys.contains(40) ||this.arrowKeys.contains(num_offset + 2))? -1:0);     
5817      this.moveOffsetX = (a==1?15:0)+(a==-1?-15:0);
5818      this.moveOffsetY = (b==1?15:0)+(b==-1?-15:0);
5819      this.setDragOffset(0,0); 
5820      this.move(this.moveOffsetX, this.moveOffsetY); 
5821      if (this.overviewmap)
5822      {
5823        this.overviewmap.moveRectanglefromMainMap(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop)
5824      }
5825      if (this.movingListener)
5826      {
5827        this.movingListener(this.origLeft-this.divLeft,this.origTop-this.divTop);
5828      }
5829      for(i=0; i < this.mapLayers.length; i++)
5830        this.mapLayers[i].scrollTiles();         
5831      this.m_scroll_id = this.setTimeout("this.arrowScroll()", 5)
5832    }   
5833    else
5834    {
5835      this.printReset();
5836      this.m_scroll_id = null;
5837      this.do_GetMinMaxLonLat();
5838      //this.infoLayer.scrollInfoLayer();
5839      this.scrollThemeBasedFOIs() ;
5840      this.scrolled = false;
5841      if (this.overviewmap)
5842      {
5843        this.overviewmap.refreshSubMap();
5844      }
5845      if (this.recenterListener)
5846      {
5847        this.recenterListener();
5848      }  
5849      MVUtil.runListeners(this.EventListeners,MVEvent.RECENTER);
5850      if (this.scalectl)
5851      {
5852        this.scalectl.update(this);
5853      }
5854    }   
5855  }  
5856    
5857  /**
5858  @private
5859  */
5860  MVMapView.prototype.dragoff = function(e)   //not used now
5861  {
5862    var Coords = this.getEventCoords(e);
5863    var mouseX = Coords.left;
5864    var mouseY = Coords.top;
5865    if (((MVGlobalVariables.browser == "NS")) && ((mouseX <= 0) || (mouseX >=
5866      this.getPaneWidth()) || (mouseY <= 0) || (mouseY >=
5867      this.getPaneHeight())) && (this.curLay))
5868    {
5869      this.mUp();
5870    }
5871  }
